[58:36.640 --> 58:37.920]  with unworkable mandates.
[58:37.920 --> 58:42.960]  Let's prioritize thoughtful planning and collaboration over arbitrary deadlines that
[58:42.960 --> 58:47.160]  would punish the shipping industry and most important of all would also punish our citizens.
[58:47.820 --> 58:48.260]  Thank you.
[58:49.960 --> 58:51.780]  Thank you, United States.
[58:53.120 --> 58:53.880]  New Alliance, please.
[58:54.980 --> 58:56.520]  Thank you, Chair.
[58:57.000 --> 58:58.060]  We thank the Secretary.
