[00:00.000 --> 00:09.440]  The total of 163 participants from 52 countries have been sponsored to attend GHG related meetings.
[00:10.720 --> 00:15.580]  For this session and the Intercessional Working Group's GHG20,
[00:16.460 --> 00:22.340]  the Trust Fund has financed the participation of delegates from 36 countries.
[00:24.140 --> 00:32.440]  Since MEPC 83, we have received financial contributions from Denmark, Germany,
[00:33.180 --> 00:40.740]  United Arab Emirates and the United Kingdom to the Voluntary Multidona Trust Fund,
[00:41.640 --> 00:49.080]  totaling approximately $500,000 US dollars. I would like to thank all the donors which,
[00:49.080 --> 00:54.860]  through their financial contributions, have facilitated and supported representative
[00:55.400 --> 01:02.960]  informed and evidence-based decision making. Finally, Mr Chair, as previously noted by the
